    "Do not explain.",
    "Choices: Atelectasis, Cardiomegaly, Consolidation, Edema, Pleural Effusion Evaluation metricUnlike the CheXpert competition which computed receiver operator curves and precision-recall curves, we elected to use sensitivity, specificity, precision and F1-score because the predictions from GPT-4V are binary.",
    "Dermatology DatasetFor evaluation of GPT-4V on the diagnosis of skin diseases, we utilize the Diverse Dermatology Images (DDI) Dataset [14].",
    "This is a publicly available histopathologically confirmed dataset that is representative of diverse skin tones.",
    "DDI contains 656 clinical images obtained from the Stanford Clinic and includes some rare dermatological conditions that have previously been described in literature [14].The Fitzpatrick skin tone (FST) was carefully labeled based on in-person visit documentation, demographic photo, and image of the lesion."
